**Miller** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous
__Basics__
The **miller** believes themself to be a civilian, but has a *true disguise* of mafioso. If there are no mafiosos in the setup, the **miller**'s *true disguise* will be an in-play mafia role. 

__Formalized__
Identity: Civilian
Starting: Process: Strongly Disguise @Self as `Mafioso` [Condition: @(Role:Mafioso) exists]
Starting: Process: Strongly Disguise @Self as @(Align:Mafia)->RandomPlayer->Role [Condition: not (@(Role:Mafioso) exists)]
